## Core Applications
- **Interactive Dashboard Creation** (30-sec PDF to dashboard conversion)
- **Game Development** (No-code game building with real-time testing)
- **Business Analytics** (Financial modeling & Monte Carlo simulations)
- **Content Generation** (SEO tools, educational content, documentation)
- **Visual Processing** (Chart analysis, image interpretation)

## Standout Features
- Available via web, mobile app, API & cloud platforms
- Free tier access on claude.ai
- Real-time code/content generation & editing
- Superior reasoning & summarization capabilities
- Visual information processing abilities
